Class ReadByteBuffer

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.thinkaurelius.titan.diskstorage.util.StaticByteBuffer
      • com.thinkaurelius.titan.diskstorage.util.ReadByteBuffer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ReadBuffer, ScanBuffer, StaticBuffer, Comparable<StaticBuffer>

    public class ReadByteBuffer
extends StaticByteBuffer
implements ReadBuffer
    Implementation of ReadBuffer against a ByteBuffer Note, that the position does not impact the state of the object. Meaning, equals, hashcode, and compare ignore the position.
    Author:
    Matthias Broecheler (me@matthiasb.com)
